---
const github = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_GITHUB
---

<div class="lg:col-span-8 lg:pl-4">
    <div class="space-y-6">
        <h1 class="font-display-lg text-headline-md md:text-display-lg text-on-surface leading-tight">
            Welcome to <span class="italic text-primary"> my labs</span>
            <br />    
            Documenting the journey, one writeup at a time.
        </h1>

        <p class="max-w-2xl text-body-md leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant">
            This is where I share writeups, technical notes, and practical workflows across Blue Team operations, SOC, DFIR, incident response, malware analysis, and everything I learn along the way.
            You can also find me on
            <a class="cursor-pointer text-primary" href={github} target="_blank"> GitHub</a>
            , where I share tools, lab environments, scripts, and code from my projects.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-2">
            <button
                class="flex cursor-pointer items-center gap-2 bg-primary px-8 py-3 font-code-sm font-bold text-on-primary-container transition-all hover:brightness-110"
            >
                &gt;_ EXPLORE ARCHIVES
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
